Class CooperativaController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.webServices.rutas.controllers.CooperativaController

  • @RestController
 @RequestMapping(value="cooperativas")
 @EnableGlobalMethodSecurity(prePostEnabled=true)

extends java.lang.Object
